## Hot Start

To start from a concrete generated state id, initialize a full variable
snapshot and call `{{ machine_class_name(model) }}_hot_start(...)`:

```c
{{ machine_class_name(model) }} machine;
{{ machine_class_name(model) }}Vars initial_vars;

{{ machine_class_name(model) }}_init(&machine);
initial_vars = *{{ machine_class_name(model) }}_vars(&machine);
